article_title: Fred Goldenberg: ACA isn’t Medicare and Medicare isn’t ACA
article_text:
Traverse City, MI (49684)

Today

Areas of patchy fog early. A mix of clouds and sun with a slight chance of thunderstorms this afternoon. High 83F. Winds light and variable. Chance of rain 30%..

Tonight

Thunderstorms likely this evening. Then the chance of scattered thunderstorms overnight. Low 66F. Winds light and variable. Chance of rain 80%.

article_metadata.author: FRED GOLDENBERG Senior Matters

og.description: There has been ongoing discussion during the last several months regarding the purported rate increase in 2016 for the BCBS Legacy Plan C Medicare Medigap coverage.
